VLNV * VLNVGenerator::getVLNV ( VLNV::IPXactType  type  ) 

Generate a vlnv that matches the user inputs.

If one of the vlnv elements is empty then a null pointer is returned. This class gives the ownership of the generated VLNV to the caller of this function.

Parameters:
type Type of the vlnv that is to be generated
Returns:
Pointer to the VLNV instance.
